snippet.title: Stolen Life - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
🔍 While working late, you hear a scream from a coworker. Rushing to investigate, you discover everyone is gone. As you search for answers, you uncover hidden secrets in your home and realize your wife is missing.

🕵️‍♂️ Explore mysterious environments, solve challenging puzzles, and unravel a gripping story that blends psychological and environmental horror. Are you ready to face the unknown?

👉 Wishlist on Steam : Stolen Life
